    <item>
      <title>塞内加尔的巴承认在总统选举中败给了竞争对手法耶</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/senegal-s-ba-concedes-defeat-in-presidential-vote-to-rival-faye</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔总统候选人阿马杜·巴承认在周日的选举中输给了反对派领导人巴西鲁·迪奥马耶·法耶，这标志着这个西非国家的政治格局发生了巨大变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/senegal-s-ba-concedes-defeat-in-presidential-vote-to-rival-faye</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 14:23:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔、AMD 因报告中国限制使用美国芯片而下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/intel-amd-fall-on-report-china-to-limit-use-of-foreign-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司和超微半导体公司的股价周一下跌，此前有报道称，中国已采取新的指导方针，限制在政府计算机中使用美国制造的微处理器和服务器。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/intel-amd-fall-on-report-china-to-limit-use-of-foreign-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 11:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟对苹果、谷歌、Meta 进行新数字法测试调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/apple-google-meta-probed-by-eu-in-test-of-new-digital-law</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧盟对苹果公司、Alphabet公司旗下谷歌和Meta Platforms公司是否遵守限制大型科技公司权力的严格新法律展开全面调查，它们面临着潜在巨额罚款的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/apple-google-meta-probed-by-eu-in-test-of-new-digital-law</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 10:06:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于投资者权衡反对派的选举势头，塞内加尔债券下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/senegal-s-bonds-sink-as-investors-weigh-opposition-s-electoral-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔的主权美元债券扭转了跌势，从当天新兴市场中表现最差的债券转为表现最好的债券，因为投资者押注这个西非国家将获得稳定的政府，而巴西鲁·迪奥马耶·法耶(Bassirou Diomaye Faye)则缓和了他在2017年期间概述的一些极端政策措施。竞选活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/senegal-s-bonds-sink-as-investors-weigh-opposition-s-electoral-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 09:32:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国宣布拨款 60 亿美元清理重工业</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/us-announces-6-billion-to-clean-up-heavy-manufacturing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拜登政府将拨款约 60 亿美元，帮助减少金属、化学品和其他难以脱碳行业的排放，包括资助建造 45 年来第一座美国新铝冶炼厂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/us-announces-6-billion-to-clean-up-heavy-manufacturing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯对乌克兰首都发动弹道导弹袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/ukraine-s-odesa-faces-power-cuts-after-more-russian-air-strikes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰当局表示，俄罗斯对基辅发动了导弹袭击，克里姆林宫加大了对敖德萨和哈尔科夫等城市以及这个饱受战争摧残的国家能源基础设施的攻击力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/ukraine-s-odesa-faces-power-cuts-after-more-russian-air-strikes</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 08:11:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩的妹妹称日本寻求朝鲜峰会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/kim-jong-un-s-sister-says-kishida-conveyed-intent-to-hold-summit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金正恩的妹妹表示，日本首相岸田文雄最近表达了“尽快”与朝鲜领导人会面的意图，此举旨在测试东京与韩国之间关系的升温。]]></description>
