    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新泽西州第一夫人退出参议院初选提振竞争对手金正恩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/nj-first-lady-tammy-murphy-suspends-campaign-for-us-senate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新泽西州第一夫人塔米·墨菲出人意料地退出民主党参议院初选，为代表安迪·金争夺四面楚歌的美国参议员罗伯特·梅南德斯所占据的席位扫清了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/nj-first-lady-tammy-murphy-suspends-campaign-for-us-senate</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 20:19:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯将成为下一任爱尔兰总理，挑战新芬党、移民问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/ireland-s-harris-set-to-become-prime-minister-in-uncontested-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，爱尔兰高等教育部长西蒙·哈里斯被任命为统一党党魁，这使他有望在几周内成为下一任总理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/ireland-s-harris-set-to-become-prime-minister-in-uncontested-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 16:42:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普在曼哈顿法院面临财务真相时刻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/trump-faces-moment-of-truth-for-his-finances-in-manhattan-court</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 周一在曼哈顿法庭就他的一起刑事案件举行听证会时，他的财务状况也面临着一个潜在的真相时刻：要么缴纳 4.54 亿美元民事欺诈判决的保释金，要么冒着纽约的风险。国家开始没收他的资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-24/trump-faces-moment-of-truth-for-his-finances-in-manhattan-court</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Mar 2024 14:08:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
